{"tid":259699,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：港男拍縮時片揚威國際 - 李八方","createTime":"2017-05-27T06:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T11:36:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3225288f2479059d7c61e01a57b8f4285d79e14","tid":259699,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T06:58:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20035367&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20035367%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170527&d=1fGj8INSxoTFNm2qpumDFJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=dceae417\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20035367%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170527&h=b680101b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20035367&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170527</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n港男拍縮時片揚威國際 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n香港攝影師蘇嘉進（Francis）再度揚威國際！佢用縮時攝影（timelapse）及超行縮影拍攝嘅短片《ESCAPE》，喺今屆葡萄牙電影藝術及旅遊節「Finisterra Arr&aacute;bida Film Art &amp; Tourism Festival」中，獲得最佳音樂視頻第二名。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\nFrancis花半年時間記錄郊外天堂同都市嘅美景。《ESCAPE》短片截圖<br />\n<br />\n呈現港美景及打工苦況<br />\n<br />\n佢話今次係首次用人物主導創作短片，能夠係芸芸高水準作品中脫穎而出，十分驚喜。<br />\n《ESCAPE》講嘅係香港人從工作地獄逃脫到郊外天堂嘅故事。Francis用咗半年時間，將中環、金鐘、尖沙嘴繁忙都市人與事，同埋飛鵝山、大澳、大帽山等美麗風景記錄低，並以人物主導，將香港人係「全球最長工時城市」打工苦況呈現。<br />\nFrancis話，香港工作環境極不平衡，每個人只係掛住工作，係生存唔係生活，其實好悲慘；又話工時過長，令人忽略好多值得去做嘅事，包括陪伴家人、花時間自我調整心靈，希望港人能夠反思。<br />\n想欣賞獲獎短片，可以去以下連結：&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/franso/videos/1333048266732449/￼\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffranso%2Fvideos%2F1333048266732449%2F%EF%BF%BC&d=1fGj8INSxoTFNm2qpumDFJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=142c4728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/franso/videos/1333048266732449/￼</a><br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=1fGj8INSxoTFNm2qpumDFJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=356e343b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"d68e1c80f52bbf86965f4e07c98922363d48c066","tid":259699,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T06:59:48.000Z","msg":"Francis花半年時間記錄郊外天堂同都市嘅美景。《ESCAPE》短片截圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170527/large/27lp2p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170527%2Flarge%2F27lp2p04.jpg&h=9e4a1ec6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09bb9ca2a748da807c5fcc4b9e920e830958dea3","tid":259699,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:15:56.000Z","msg":"睇錯左港男縮陽揚威國際"},{"pid":"8c845c696f03adfff8590d87c80f42fc481f64b1","tid":259699,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"家下效野都多人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nD人群又無品無修養<br />\n<br />\n勁滋騷人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都無得放鬆"},{"pid":"c55760ce80bddc998974cb36e84c558f671d1859","tid":259699,"uid":12944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:25:31.000Z","msg":"睇錯左縮陽片🤦🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"7225ba4ac284bfff17663a6a536a455cce96e58d","tid":259699,"uid":12944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:25:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯左港男縮陽揚威國際</blockquote><br />\n+1"},{"pid":"513a0dadd69025956b1f0427986c760522e6e424","tid":259699,"uid":21008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:36:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇錯左港男縮陽揚威國際</blockquote><br />\n+1</blockquote><br />\n <br />\